-- Greek Police Arrest Man Who Fired Shots in Athens Tax Office
-- B y   E l e n i   C h r e p a
-- 2012-03-19T10:44:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-19/greek-police-arrest-man-who-fired-shots-in-athens-tax-office.html
Greek police arrested an armed man
who entered a tax office in Agia Paraskevi, in the suburbs of
 Athens , at midday today and opened fire, according to a text
message from the Athens police press office. No injuries were
reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eleni Chrepa in Athens at 
